Module Name:

    dirs.

Abstract:

    This file specifies the subdirectories of the current directory that
    contain component makefiles.


NOTE:   Commented description of this file is in \nt\bak\bin\dirs.tpl

NOTE:   grovmsg subdirectory must be first in dirs list, because it builds
        grovmsg.h, which is included by all.hxx of all other directories'
        sources

!ENDIF

DIRS=grovmsg  \
     grovctrl \
     groveler \
     grovperf

